body:
I cannot reproduce this issue using the `master` branch.
Did you modified the Dockerfile [here](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/Dockerfile) in any way?
From the error message, it seem that the 3rd command, instead of being [this](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/Dockerfile#L13-L19) is just `RUN`. Did you added a new line in the file ?
